{"tid":2231845,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍基地現「基隆市政府」","createTime":"2020-10-06T03:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T05:36:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f91a7108f9777b806463a7e3bb74453b33517410","tid":2231845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201006/ZSXUFJXSHNFOXGEJVUC67M5P3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201006%2FZSXUFJXSHNFOXGEJVUC67M5P3Q%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL1RUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=672d233f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201006%2FZSXUFJXSHNFOXGEJVUC67M5P3Q%2F&h=27e78d17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201006/ZSXUFJXSHNFOXGEJVUC67M5P3Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n解放軍基地現「基隆市政府」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jQQ2NXAiPn7aDdI0J9f7K6X8fZ0=/1423x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7TDKYGCHWBEE7IJVO2DVYAKXOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjQQ2NXAiPn7aDdI0J9f7K6X8fZ0%3D%2F1423x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7TDKYGCHWBEE7IJVO2DVYAKXOQ.jpg&h=85a264c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■解放軍軍訓基地赫見模擬「基隆市政府」的建築。<br />\n<br />\n台灣今年的雙十節晚會首度移師基隆舉行，於本月9日登場，而內地網昨日卻流傳解放軍在模擬「基隆市政府」進行演習，掀起台灣民眾討論。在兩岸關係日益緊張之時，台媒日前的民調指出，如果兩岸爆發衝突，44.9%的台灣民眾願意上戰場，相較7月增加四個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n44.9%台民眾願上戰場<br />\n<br />\n按照慣例，台灣總統蔡英文將會出席雙十晚會。然而內地先前卻流出，解放軍軍訓基地出現模擬「基隆市政府」的仿造建築。有鑑大陸近來對台軍事恐嚇加劇，「基隆市政府」的出現，引發網民討論基隆市政府是否解放軍的重點打擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，大陸並非首次在軍訓基地中仿造台灣政府機關的建築，如內蒙古朱日和訓練基地數年前曾被揭建有模擬「台灣總統府」。<br />\n<br />\n台媒前日的民調顯示，如果兩岸爆發衝突，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部昨日向立法院發送的業務報告首次證實，台軍為應對敵情變化，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中共為彰顯解放軍機師駕駛戰機的技術，《解放軍報》昨日繪聲繪影發佈。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網 /《解放軍報》"},{"pid":"e12766bd23e695baa5c48b9a2a06fdbb95a41537","tid":2231845,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"而家台灣人開始了解到<br />\n上戰場基本上係一面倒屠殺支那蟲<br />\n梗係制"},{"pid":"5d3cef120df781c926da2b326644a4cea2482752","tid":2231845,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e12766bd23e695baa5c48b9a2a06fdbb95a41537","tid":2231845,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"而家台灣人開始了解到<br />\n上戰場基本上係一面倒屠殺支那蟲<br />\n梗係制"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb0c40e8e52cf4d47842a6a6b7c88963f25df8","tid":2231845,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"最驚就係支那間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}